{
  "stem": "10768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 28.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you have to stay in a line to get a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to register.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When your come there to register, first of all, bread, it was not available.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If somebody had a piece of bread, a lot of it was black market, which we couldn't afford to buy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we came to register, they said, in Tashkent you cannot remain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We don't have room for you in Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There is an awful lot of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We are not able to provide the people with food or with jobs, or with nothing else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they told us to go on a train and go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was from Turkmenia, they sent us to Tajikistan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we came to a town, which was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Chardjou. ?] And this was-- let me find out when this was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was 1942-- the end of 1942, sometimes December 1942.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we came December, 19-- to, to Chardjou, again, we went to register.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They told us-- and we had no documents, nothing to show, just whatever we told them what our past was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to Chardjou, we registered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, you cannot remain in the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The town is swollen up with refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We cannot provide you with anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can go to work about 30 kilometers, or 40 kilometers from Chardjou on a railroad-- railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you will get 800 gram of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What did we think?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We needed the 800 gram of bread just to keep ourselves alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew it's not going to be cold there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So whatever we had-- the three of us, my brother, which was younger than I am, and Rachel, who was my cousin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was four year younger than I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
